<m0>Campus editor besieged by 2nd-guessers<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .78 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .423 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
<m1><styl>kr,0<ql>
<styl>ruleron<ql>
<styl>txt,1<ql>
